{"tid":2219884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"干預加拿大內政？ 中國駐加大使促加方立即釋放孟晚舟","createTime":"2020-09-27T07:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T15:07:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"901bf4fe9cdcccae2f324aa2badaed97c2e68890","tid":2219884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551867-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551867-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=08b5ceb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551867-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=04d5b374\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551867-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國駐加拿大大使叢培武表示，中加關係遇到很大困難，根源在於中國電訊設備商華為副董事長孟晚舟事件，兩國自貿協定談判進程亦因為加方的干擾停滯，強調孟晚舟沒有違反加拿大法律，事件帶有政治屬性，敦促加方立即釋放孟晚舟，為兩國關係重回正軌創造條件。<br />\n<br />\n叢培武又批評，美國對外採取的單邊制裁和長臂管轄，不單止針對華為，還將矛頭對準微信、TikTok等中國高科技公司，表明美方的真實意圖是要打壓中國企業，十分危險。<br />\n<br />\n談及中國的人權狀況，叢培武說，涉港等問題不是人權問題，實施港區國安法是為堵塞香港在維護國家安全的漏洞。"},{"pid":"a5e3d4583b4b3387e4c1494d0a4b9de56d806d3b","tid":2219884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}